subject: Re:Investment Partnership,

subject: Re:Investment Partnership,
body:
Hello Alex,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm quite intrigued by your proposal and would love to hear more about it. Could you please provide some more details about the investment opportunity? What kind of business is your client interested in?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Tracy
